room_title: Escape room "File X: Area 51 Incident" by Escape Room Westford in Boston
room_description: Under the cover of darkness, to avoid discovery by the press, a covert operation took place to move the contents of the top-secret base known as Area 51. Thought to contain the nation’s deepest secrets, every object was moved to this very place and now it’s up to you and your group to discover the mysteries hidden for decades!
